    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but youre kind of dodging the other side of it tho. if people don't have a sense of national identity or loyalty to their own community, doesn't that just lead to a total breakdown of society? like how can a country even function or have any stability if everyone is just focusing on globalism and has no specific commitment to their fellow citizens? isn't that just a recipe for chaos?",
